POE-Component-App-PNGCrush

The module is a non-blocking wrapper around L<App::PNGCrush>
which provides interface to ``pngcrush'' program. See documentation for
L<App::PNGCrush> regarding information on how to obtain ``pngcrush''
program.

You should familiarize yourself with C<new()>, C<run()> and C<set_options()>
methods of L<App::PNGCrush> module to fully understand the workings
of this POE wrapper.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc POE::Component::App::PNGCrush

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=POE-Component-App-PNGCrush

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/POE-Component-App-PNGCrush

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/POE-Component-App-PNGCrush

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/POE-Component-App-PNGCrush


